      "kind": "structural",
      "auto_safe": false,
      "priority": "P2",
      "status": "pending",
      "prompt": "GDD section 9 Tier 4 Wonders Effect column drifts from shipped code on every row and needs author judgement on which design wins. Cornucopia: GDD says +5.0 Provisions/s + cap halo, code is 4.0 Provisions/s no cap halo. Perpetual Engine: GDD says +50 Power capacity, code is 5.0 Power/s + 60 Coal seed. Pyre: GDD says noise emitter, 5000 HP, emergency wave; code is -6/min Terror credit, 1200 HP. Sanctum: GDD says -20/min Terror, code is +1 HP/s/unit map-wide heal. Decision needed: amend section 9 to match code, or rewrite code to match section 9.",
      "source": "2026-05-16 canonical audit"
    },
